00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Trimming my Natural Hair

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:10.500
I combed my freshly washed hair and put it into twists.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:13.500
Now we trim the hair!

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:16.500
Just joking!

